sequenceDiagram
    participant Order
    participant PaymentService
    participant SellerService
    participant Database
    participant CronJob
    participant BankAPI

    Order->>PaymentService: Payment Succeeded
    PaymentService->>SellerService: Process Earnings
    SellerService->>SellerService: Calculate Split
    Note over SellerService: Platform: 12%<br/>Gateway: 2.5%<br/>Logistics: $5<br/>Tax: 2%<br/>Reserve: 1%
    SellerService->>Database: Add to Pending Balance
    SellerService->>Database: Create Ledger Entry
    SellerService->>Database: Create Escrow Record
    
    Note over CronJob: Every Minute
    CronJob->>Database: Check Pending Escrows
    Database-->>CronJob: Ready for Release
    CronJob->>Database: Move to Available Balance
    CronJob->>Database: Update Ledger
    
    Seller->>Database: Request Payout
    Database->>SellerService: Execute Payout
    SellerService->>Database: Lock Balance
    SellerService->>BankAPI: Transfer Funds
    alt Success
        BankAPI-->>SellerService: Success
        SellerService->>Database: Mark as Completed
        SellerService->>Database: Update Paid Balance
        SellerService->>Database: Create Ledger Entry
    else Failure
        BankAPI-->>SellerService: Error
        SellerService->>Database: Mark as Failed
        SellerService->>Database: Unlock Balance
        SellerService->>Database: Schedule Retry
    end
